title: Heaven Raw Cafe
description: Raw food cafe at Fern Community Garden - added cooked food in late-2014 to include a vegan bowl, nachos, burger, and hot dog. Raw items include wraps, pizza, quiche, enchilada, burgers, juices, smoothies, salads, and sweets. Raw food is gluten free. Monday night (5:30pm-7:30pm) it's open for 'Soupi' only which is a by donation meal. Thursday and Saturday nights are by donation meals and cafe. Friday night special is tacos. Wednesday is movie night.
